      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "まるでゲームの中から出てきたみたいで……そうか\nだからゲームのセリフが聞こえたのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s like you stepped right out of the game… I see\nMaybe that's why I thought I heard a line from the game.",
        "id": ""
